author":"ubuntu","text":"Blocked on manifest/edition fixes before wiring StatusRequest handler; IPC schema aligned and tested.","created_at":"2025-11-21T00:49:18Z"},{"id":126,"issue_id":"ultrasearch-c00.8.4","author":"ubuntu","text":"WhiteStone in_progress: set status defaults to 'initializing' and enabled /metrics HTTP endpoint (uses cfg.metrics.bind). Workspace check green after adding tempfile/memmap2 deps to workspace + core-serialization.","created_at":"2025-11-21T03:00:02Z"},{"id":128,"issue_id":"ultrasearch-c00.8.4","author":"ubuntu","text":"Added init_basic_status_provider + global update helpers (volumes/state/metrics/queue/last_commit) so other modules can push status without carrying handle. Status still defaults to initializing; cargo check green.","created_at":"2025-11-21T03:01:44Z"},{"id":129,"issue_id":"ultrasearch-c00.8.4","author":"ubuntu","text":"SchedulerRuntime now updates status + metrics (queue depth, active_workers, state) using new helper exports; service main wires init_basic_status_provider() + spawn_metrics_http(). Workspace check still green.","created_at":"2025-11-21T03:07:39Z"},{"id":137,"issue_id":"ultrasearch-c00.8.4","author":"ubuntu","text":"SchedulerRuntime now pushes queue depth + active workers + state into StatusProvider and metrics (using global snapshot). Added /metrics TCP server already; service main uses init_basic_status_provider() + clap config. Build green.","created_at":"2025-11-21T03:12:51Z"}]}
